🎬 Movie Ticket Booking System

A simple Python-based Movie Ticket Booking System built using Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts.

This project allows users to:
Book movie tickets
Cancel booked tickets
Update seat numbers
View ticket information

It is a beginner-friendly project to practice:
Python Classes & Objects
Encapsulation
Methods
Constructors
Basic Ticket Management Logic

🚀 Features
✅ Book a movie ticket
✅ Cancel a booked ticket
✅ Update seat number
✅ Display ticket information
✅ Uses private attributes for data security

💡 Concepts Used
Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)
Encapsulation using private variables
Class methods
Conditional statements
Lists in Python
